v 3
d residualundoc: Residual-method estimator of the undocumented (unauthorized) immigrant population.
d
d Implements the residual method U = C - L (Warren, Warren & Zheng 2023): survey-
d measured noncitizens C minus a reconstructed legal noncitizen population L.
d Five subcommands in one command:
d   interp       anchor interpolation of theta = U/C over time
d   apply        cross-sectional: one theta across units (e.g. states), with
d                optional benchmarking against a direct estimate and a confidence
d                interval combining sampling error and cross-source spread
d   direct       Warren-style year-by-year reconstruction of L
d   transport    transport a survey rate to a benchmark on the odds/logit/ratio scale
d   triangulate  side-by-side comparison of residual-method sources at one year
d
d Requires: Stata 15 or later.
d Author:   Eric Booth, Texas 2036 (eric.booth at texas2036.org)
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260703
f residualundoc.ado
f residualundoc_interp.ado
f residualundoc_apply.ado
f residualundoc_direct.ado
f residualundoc_transport.ado
f residualundoc_triangulate.ado
f residualundoc.sthlp
f example_residualundoc.do
